Get camera operation matrix

Source: R/get_cam_op.R
get_cam_op.Rd

This function returns the camera operation matrix as returned by camtrapR's function cameraOperation().

get_cam_op(datapkg, ...)

Arguments

datapkg

a camera trap data package object, as returned by read_camtrap_dp().

...

filter predicates for filtering on deployments

Value

a matrix. Row names always indicate the locationName (station ID) "Station"+locationName. Column names are dates.

Details

The deployment data are grouped by locationName (station ID in camtrapR jargon). If multiple deploymnts are linked to same location, daily efforts higher than one occur.

get_cam_op(mica)
